<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. The sampling site and habitat of B. jayabhumi sp. nov.: A. Sampling site indicated with white circle (○); B. The entrance of the cave; C. Dripping water from the plant roots penetrating from the surface; D. pool on stalagmite." , "Figure 6. Bryocyclops jayabhumi sp. nov., adult male: A. P 1; B. P 2; C. P 3; D. P 4." , "Figure 3. Bryocyclops jayabhumi sp. nov., adult female: A. Antennule; B. Antenna; C. Mandible; D. Maxillule; E. Maxilla; F. Maxilliped; G. Egg sacs on genital double-somite; H. Pair of spermatophore; I. Genital double-somite, ventral view." , "Figure 5. Bryocyclops jayabhumi sp. nov., adult male: A. Habitus, dorsal view; B. Urosome, dorsal view; C. Urosome, ventral view; D. Urosome (without pediger 5), lateral view; E. Antennule." , "Figure 2. Bryocyclops jayabhumi sp. nov., SEM photographs of adult female: A. Habitus, dorsal view; B. Cephalothorax and pediger 2, dorsal view; C. Pediger 4 - 5 and genital double-somite, dorsal view; D. Urosome (without pediger 5), ventral view; E. Urosome 3 - 5 and caudal rami, dorsal view; F. P 5 on pediger 5, dorsal view; G. Urosome 4 - 5 and caudal rami, ventral view; H-I. Left and right P 6 on genital double-somite, dorsal view." , "Figure 4. Bryocyclops jayabhumi sp. nov., adult female: A. P 1; B. P 2; C. P 3; D. P 4; E. P 5." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/504926" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/504927" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/504930" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/504925" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/504928" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/504929" .

